thread.title: KIM NAUGLE
thread.title_full: Superior Van and Mobility reviewed by KIM NAUGLE

author: KIM NAUGLE
title: KIM NAUGLE
text: This is more of an overall review as the service I had that generated this survey is still in process as they have to get a part from Braun for a warranty repair. In general, Superior in Lexington Kentucky has always done all they can to meet my service needs and they have done it with concern for my convenience. I would and do recommend them often.
